summary:
Sarah Norris is a creative, independent English language trainer, editor and translator. A native speaker with an imaginative, flexible approach coupled with a passion for language. She teaches:

•	Academic English
•	Confidence and fluency through drama
•	Creative writing and speaking
•	Cambridge Exam Preparation (FCE, CAE, CPE, IELTS)

She also edits academic articles and theses; translates and edits website content (Dutch > English) and is a speaking examiner for the leading international English exam and assessment organisation.
